[23:46] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'generate 3D geometry, separate step, you were able to split it into the parts, which was also one of the first to introduce. Then the most beloved thing that time was low poly mods, which'

[23:58] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'was featuring that polygen 1.0, that allowed to read topology, high poly into low poly, and sometimes results were very impressive. And it\'s still one of the best low'

[24:11] [scene:talk]
