[24:25] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: '-free ovoxel structure. Trellis shows a real revolution. When I saw that result, I was actually like, oh my God, I need to make video right now. That\'s like historical event. And I was actually'

[24:37] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'right about it. It is definitely the best model still for the open source. And what was even shocking, they were first to introduce the transparency and translucency support, right? You were able to'

[24:49] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
