[25:14] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'Trellis, Hunion 2.1, or anything else and refine it into cleaner high detail geometry. So combinations like Trellis 2.0 plus UltraShape 1.0 was actually dominating in terms of'

[25:26] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'comfy UI setups or any local setups. And you could run that on 24 gigabyte VRAM on consumer\'s grade GPU, which was amazing. So in 2025, we got very close to'

[25:39] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
